fm: void BtaAudioContent::start(const arb::AppMode& app_mode, arb::Factor factor, const arb::Param& param, void* frm_param) { 	//BTAAPP_EXT_API_START;  	medsrv_ntf_media_status_t* media_status_t =  		GET_BTAUDIO_MEDIA_MANAGEMENT()->getMediaStatus(); 	//BTAAPP_FUNC("[%d]", media_status_t->post_status.status);  	bool AvpConnectStatus = GET_BTAUDIO_MEDIA_MANAGEMENT()->getAvpConnectFlag(); 	bool AvrcpConnectStatus = GET_BTAUDIO_MEDIA_MANAGEMENT()->getAvrcpConnectFlag();  	//Processing Resume Play Request 	if(((AvpConnectStatus) || (AvrcpConnectStatus)) && 		((MEDSRV_MS_PLAYABLE == media_status_t->post_status.status) ||  		 (MEDSRV_MS_AVAILABLE == media_status_t->post_status.status)) && 		(BTA_RESUME_NOT_INVOKED == GET_MCSR_PLAYBACK_INSTANCE()->getResumeInvokeState())) 	{ 		bta_resume_invoke_src resume_invoke_src = {}; 		resume_invoke_src.btaResumeReqSrc = BTA_RESUME_AUD_CONTENT_ENTRY; 		//AudioコンテントSTART時は強制Play 		GET_MCSR_PLAYPAUSE_INSTANCE()->setResumePlayType(MEDSRV_RPT_STD); 		FRM_apl_sndmsg(EVT_BTAUDIO_SRVBRIDGE_RESUME_PLAY_REQ,  				APPMAIN_BLKID_BTA_SRVBRIDGE,  				&resume_invoke_src,  				sizeof(resume_invoke_src)); 	} 	 	GET_BTAUDIO_MEDIA_MANAGEMENT()->setBtaAudioMode(true); 	GET_BTAUDIO_MEDIA_MANAGEMENT()->setBtAudio_suspend_mode(false);     if(true == GET_BTAUDIO_MEDIA_MANAGEMENT()->getVRModeState())    {     medsrv_ntf_play_info_t* playInfo =         GET_MCSR_PLAY_INFO_INSTANCE()->getPlayInfo();          if((true == playInfo->post_info.f_pause))         {             playInfo->post_info.f_pause = false;              FRM_apl_sndmsg(EVT_STC_BTAUDIO_PAUSE_STATE_NOTI,                            APPMAIN_BLKID_BTA_STC,                            playInfo,                            sizeof(medsrv_ntf_play_info_t));         }     } 	CompleteStart(); 	//BTAAPP_EXT_API_END; }

fm: void BtaAudioContent::resume(const arb::AppMode& app_mode, void* frm_param) { 	//BTAAPP_EXT_API_START;     medsrv_ntf_media_status_t* media_status_t =         GET_BTAUDIO_MEDIA_MANAGEMENT()->getMediaStatus();      if(((MEDSRV_MS_PLAYABLE == media_status_t->post_status.status) ||         (MEDSRV_MS_AVAILABLE == media_status_t->post_status.status)) &&         (BTA_RESUME_NOT_INVOKED == GET_MCSR_PLAYBACK_INSTANCE()->getResumeInvokeState()))     {         // Call has ended, start the playback         bta_resume_invoke_src resume_invoke_src = {};         resume_invoke_src.btaResumeReqSrc = BTA_RESUME_HFP_CALL_END;         FRM_apl_sndmsg(EVT_BTAUDIO_SRVBRIDGE_RESUME_PLAY_REQ, 		        APPMAIN_BLKID_BTA_SRVBRIDGE, 		        &resume_invoke_src, 		        sizeof(resume_invoke_src));       }     else     {         //BTAAPP_FUNC("[%d]",             // media_status_t->post_status.status);     } 	GET_BTAUDIO_MEDIA_MANAGEMENT()->setBtaAudioMode(true); 	GET_BTAUDIO_MEDIA_MANAGEMENT()->setBtAudio_suspend_mode(false); 	CompleteStart(); 	//BTAAPP_EXT_API_END; }

fm: void BtaAudioContent::suspend(const arb::AppMode& app_mode, void* frm_param) { 	//BTAAPP_EXT_API_START;      medsrv_ntf_media_status_t* media_status_t =         GET_BTAUDIO_MEDIA_MANAGEMENT()->getMediaStatus();     bool bCompleteStopFlag = true;      // FRM_apl_killtimer(APPMAIN_BLKID_BTA_STC,     //                 EVT_STC_BTA_RESUME_BANNER_RETRY_TIMER_EXPIRY,     //                 BTA_RESUME_BANNER_RETRY_TIMER_UNIQUE_SEQ_NUMBER);      if(MEDSRV_MS_DISCONNECT != media_status_t->post_status.status)     { 		/* If call is on same device send Stop command additionally  		 * to the device */ 		if(GET_BTAUDIO_MEDIA_MANAGEMENT()->isCallOnSameDevice()) 		{ 			//Call other SendStopCommand 			GET_BTAUDIO_MEDIA_MANAGEMENT()->setCallOnSameDevice(false); 			FRM_apl_sndmsg(EVT_BTAUDIO_SRVBRIDGE_SEND_STOP_COMMAND_HFP_REQ,                 APPMAIN_BLKID_BTA_SRVBRIDGE,                 NULL,                 0); 		}  		FRM_apl_sndmsg(EVT_BTAUDIO_SRVBRIDGE_STOP_PLAY_REQ, 			APPMAIN_BLKID_BTA_SRVBRIDGE, 			NULL, 			0);          bCompleteStopFlag = false;     }     else     {         //BTAAPP_FUNC("[%d]",             // media_status_t->post_status.status);     }      if(bCompleteStopFlag)     { 		GET_BTAUDIO_MEDIA_MANAGEMENT()->setBtaAudioMode(false); 		CompleteStop();  		/* Restart timer to hold NPS contents for a duration of 		 * BTA_STOP_PLAY_FLICKER_TIMEOUT_VALUE_IN_MSEC 		 * before clearing it 		 **/ 		FRM_apl_killtimer(APPMAIN_BLKID_BTA_STC, 						EVT_STC_BTAUDIO_STOP_PLAY_WAIT_CLEAR_EXPIRY, 						BTA_STOP_PLAY_WAIT_CLEAR_TIMER_UNIQUE_SEQ_NUMBER);  		FRM_apl_killtimer(APPMAIN_BLKID_BTA_STC, 						EVT_STC_BTAUDIO_STOP_PLAY_CLEAR_DISPLAY_EXPIRY, 						BTA_STOP_PLAY_CLEAR_DISPLAY_TIMER_UNIQUE_SEQ_NUMBER);  		FRM_apl_settimer(APPMAIN_BLKID_BTA_STC, 						EVT_STC_BTAUDIO_STOP_PLAY_WAIT_CLEAR_EXPIRY, 						BTA_STOP_PLAY_WAIT_CLEAR_TIMER_UNIQUE_SEQ_NUMBER, 						FRM_TIMER_USN, 						BTA_STOP_PLAY_WAIT_CLEAR_TIMEOUT_VALUE_IN_MSEC);     } 	GET_BTAUDIO_MEDIA_MANAGEMENT()->setBtAudio_suspend_mode(true); 	// SUSPEND前の再生情報を格納、SUSPEND中のMute連動Pause判定に使用 	GET_MCSR_PLAYPAUSE_INSTANCE()->storePlayInfoBeforeSuspend(); 	//BTAAPP_EXT_API_END; }

fm: void BtaAudioContent::end(const arb::AppMode& app_mode, void* frm_param) { 	//BTAAPP_EXT_API_START; 	medsrv_ntf_media_status_t* media_status_t =  		GET_BTAUDIO_MEDIA_MANAGEMENT()->getMediaStatus(); 	bool bCompleteStopFlag = true;      // FRM_apl_killtimer(APPMAIN_BLKID_BTA_STC,     //                 EVT_STC_BTA_RESUME_BANNER_RETRY_TIMER_EXPIRY,     //                 BTA_RESUME_BANNER_RETRY_TIMER_UNIQUE_SEQ_NUMBER);  	if(MEDSRV_MS_DISCONNECT != media_status_t->post_status.status) 	{ 		FRM_apl_sndmsg(EVT_BTAUDIO_SRVBRIDGE_STOP_PLAY_REQ,  				APPMAIN_BLKID_BTA_SRVBRIDGE,  				NULL,  				0); 		bCompleteStopFlag = false; 	} 	else 	{ 		GET_MCSR_PLAYBACK_INSTANCE()->setResumeInvokeState(BTA_RESUME_NOT_INVOKED);	//	RTC#758247対応 		//BTAAPP_FUNC("[%d]",  			// media_status_t->post_status.status); 	} 	 	if(bCompleteStopFlag) 	{ 		GET_BTAUDIO_MEDIA_MANAGEMENT()->setBtaAudioMode(false); 		CompleteStop();          		/* Restart timer to hold NPS contents for a duration of 		 * BTA_STOP_PLAY_FLICKER_TIMEOUT_VALUE_IN_MSEC 		 * before clearing it 		 **/ 		FRM_apl_killtimer(APPMAIN_BLKID_BTA_STC, 						EVT_STC_BTAUDIO_STOP_PLAY_WAIT_CLEAR_EXPIRY, 						BTA_STOP_PLAY_WAIT_CLEAR_TIMER_UNIQUE_SEQ_NUMBER);  		FRM_apl_killtimer(APPMAIN_BLKID_BTA_STC, 						EVT_STC_BTAUDIO_STOP_PLAY_CLEAR_DISPLAY_EXPIRY, 						BTA_STOP_PLAY_CLEAR_DISPLAY_TIMER_UNIQUE_SEQ_NUMBER);  		FRM_apl_settimer(APPMAIN_BLKID_BTA_STC, 						EVT_STC_BTAUDIO_STOP_PLAY_WAIT_CLEAR_EXPIRY, 						BTA_STOP_PLAY_WAIT_CLEAR_TIMER_UNIQUE_SEQ_NUMBER, 						FRM_TIMER_USN, 						BTA_STOP_PLAY_WAIT_CLEAR_TIMEOUT_VALUE_IN_MSEC);         	}     GET_BTAUDIO_MEDIA_MANAGEMENT()->setBtAudio_suspend_mode(false); 	GET_MCSR_PLAYPAUSE_INSTANCE()->setResumePlayType(MEDSRV_RPT_STD); 	//BTAAPP_EXT_API_END; }

frm_param) {     //BTAAPP_EXT_API_START;     app_param_t *app_param = (app_param_t*)individual_data.data;     /* 画面コンテントオン遷移中にする、遷移中にONS表示要求が発生した場合に保留し、遷移完了通知後に表示を行う */ GET_BTA_MODE_CONTROLLER()->setSuspendMode(BTA_VR_SUSPEND_CANCEL);     bool b_QLEntryCheck = false;      if (arb::BACK == factor)     {         if(NULL != frm_param)         {             int formId = *(int *)frm_param;             //BTAAPP_FUNC("[%d]",formId);              switch(formId)             {                 case FRM_MN_BT_W_02_01_02:                 {                     FRM_apl_sndmsg(EVT_BTA_MODECTRL_VISUALOTHER_BACK_TRANS,                                     APPMAIN_BLKID_BTA_MODECTRL,                                     NULL,                                     0);                 }                 break;                 case FRM_ME_BT_W_01_01:                 {                     FRM_apl_sndmsg(EVT_BTA_MODECTRL_VISUALOTHER_QL_BACK_TRANS, fm: void BtaOtherVisualContent::end(const arb::AppMode& app_mode, void* frm_param) {     //BTAAPP_EXT_API_START;     medsrv_ntf_media_status_t* media_status_t =         GET_BTAUDIO_MEDIA_MANAGEMENT()->getMediaStatus();     bta_screen_id_t current_screen_id = GET_VDC_VC_STATUS_REGISTER()->getBtaCurrentScreen();      /* 画面コンテントオン遷移中情報初期化 */     GET_BTAUDIO_MEDIA_MANAGEMENT()->setInScreenTransitionProgress(false);     GET_BTAUDIO_MEDIA_MANAGEMENT()->setBtaVisualOtherMode(false);     FRM_apl_sndmsg(EVT_BTA_MODECTRL_STOP_OTHER_VISUAL_CONTENT,                     APPMAIN_BLKID_BTA_MODECTRL,                     &current_screen_id,                     sizeof(current_screen_id));      /*Status bar code*/     if((MEDSRV_MS_DISCONNECT != media_status_t->post_status.status) &&         (true == GET_BTAUDIO_MEDIA_MANAGEMENT()->isBtaAudioModeOn()))     {         bta_statusBar_info info;         info.type = BTA_VISUAL_OTHER_MODE_ON;         info.config = CLOCK_ONLY;          // FRM_apl_sndmsg(EVT_STC_BTAUDIO_UPDATE_STATUS_BAR,         //                     APPMAIN_BLKID_BTA_STC,         //                     &info,         //                     sizeof(info));     }      //BTAAPP_EXT_API_END; }
